			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="In this dialogue, Lur Xanta is trying to convince the other 3 to leave with her to join the cult of Lolth.&#xD;&#xA;Player can help her convince them, or fail to do so and they will attack Lur Xanta for being disloyal.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;This dialogue has 2 outcomes:&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;AGGRO: Lur Jox (or another spider) attacks Lur Xanta, killing her in one shot. (via gameplay - not cine)&#xD;&#xA;PEACEFUL: Lur Xanta convinces the other 3 to follow her into the Underdark-- they are leaving to somewhere new.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;Lur Xanta is fantatical and somewhat learned. The other 3 are a bit more simple." />
